%% Diagram: HTML5 drag-and-drop event flow
%% Type: sequenceDiagram
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant Source as Source element
    participant Target as Drop target
    participant DT as DataTransfer

    User->>Source: mousedown + drag
    Source->>DT: dragstart (read/write)
    Note over DT: setData / setDragImage<br/>only chance to write
    Source-->>Source: drag (repeats)

    User->>Target: pointer enters
    Target->>DT: dragenter (protected)
    Note over Target: preventDefault to accept

    loop while over target
        Target->>DT: dragover (protected)
        Note over Target: preventDefault every time<br/>set dropEffect
    end

    alt user releases over target
        Target->>DT: drop (read-only)
        Note over DT: getData reads payload
        Source->>Source: dragend
    else user releases off-target or Esc
        Source->>Source: dragend
        Note over Source: dropEffect = none
    end
